  "detailed_description": "<h1>IN PRESS</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“Baby Walking Simulator is a simulator about a baby. A baby who must walk.”</i></p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PC GAMER</strong></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Take control of a baby!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Walk by holding and releasing a single button!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Defeat yourself and other players!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136880/extras/64e75b21575c723d19c38e2236494d35.poster.avif?t=1768148622\" width=625 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136880/extras/64e75b21575c723d19c38e2236494d35.webm?t=1768148622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
